ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 219, British Columbia
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 219 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the Minister to provide financial assistance to the province of BRITISH COLUMBIA, with respect to the interface fires that occurred from May 23 to October 26, 2018.
